callToAction: NSLOCTEXT("", "4B0DC61D4C1780CBDD48F78FF6DF658F", "Seek and destroy Malgus, the Djinn Demon.")
description: NSLOCTEXT("", "8F645BFE46E4668DD0D69986162DFD5F", "The Tower Arcana has reappeared, but this time with a stowaway! An extremely powerful Djinn named Malgus has escaped imprisonment in the far future and now plots the eradication of all Verrans. Fortunately, he used most of his power to energize the Intra-Sphere so it could finally go backwards in time and space. This means there is a window of opportunity to track him down and destroy him before he regains power.")
name: MIQ_0015_BFP_BetrayalOfFuturePast
